1. box
    a. rectangles for layout and collision
    b. "Axis-Aligned Bounding Boxes" or "AABBs"
2. functions:
    a. display (kind of box)
        i.  inline
    b. width and height
    c. margin 
        i. margin: 0 auto; centering
    d. padding (soace around and inside box)
        i. 1 left right
        ii. 2 left right // up bottom
        iii. 更多 上右下左
    d. border    
        i. width, style, color, radius
    e. background
    f. typography
        i. t-family
        ii. font-size
        iii. font-weight
        iv. line-height
        v. color
        vi. text-align
3. unit
    a. pixels
    b. percentages
    c. viewport: 100vw/uh phone screen size
    d. em/rem mobile friendly, relative to font size


